{%- comment -%}
  step — one numbered step: a number, a title, and a body line. Shared markup
  across sections; each host section styles the `.step` / `.step__num` /
  `.step__title` / `.step__text` classes within its own wrapper, so a size-guide
  step and a storage row reuse one markup source while keeping their own look.
  → COMPONENTS.md

  Params: num, title, body (req-ish); attrs (opt) — block.shopify_attributes
{%- endcomment -%}
<div class="step" {{ attrs }}>
  <span class="step__num">{{ num }}</span>
  <div class="step__body">
    <h3 class="step__title">{{ title }}</h3>
    <p class="step__text">{{ body }}</p>
  </div>
</div>
